prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D artwork for a greeting card. A humorous and vibrant watercolor painting of the couple from the reference photo, transformed into charming cartoon characters. The scene is a chaotic but loving birthday party preparation. Lao Lao, in her white dress, is precariously balancing on a wobbly stool, trying to hang a "Happy Birthday" banner that's hilariously tangled. Jordan, still in his graduation gown but with the cap askew, is on one knee, not proposing, but offering her a single, slightly squashed cupcake with a lit candle, a look of playful urgency on his face. In the background, instead of a gate, there's a whimsical, leaning birthday cake with too many candles, and colorful balloons are escaping towards the ceiling. The colors are soft and blended with visible brushstrokes, creating a lighthearted and joyful atmosphere. In the center, in a beautiful, flowing, dark blue handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!".
